NAME: raw_counts_to_cps

PURPOSE: Used in COUNTS_TO_IRR to convert from counts to irradiance. This routine determines the integration time and binsize and adjusts the counts array appropriately.

USAGE: out=raw_counts_to_cps(raw_counts,time,binsize)

OPTIONAL INPUT KEYWORDS:

VERBOSE : Set if reporting of details is desired

Parameters

raw_counts
time
binsize
